opennlp.ccg.alignment
Class MappingGroup

java.lang.Object
  opennlp.ccg.alignment.MappingGroup
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<MappingGroup>
public class MappingGroup
extends Object
implements Comparable<MappingGroup>

Class for representing groups of mappings during reading or writing. Mapping groups encapsulate a phrase number (usually associated with a phrase's line number) and a number of mappings in the group (its length).

Author:
Scott Martin
